        <Slider Canvas.Top="604" DataContext="{Binding Source={StaticResource Locator}, Path=RingVolumeViewModel}" Minimum="{Binding MinValue}" Maximum="{Binding MaxValue}" Value="{Binding CurrentValue}"/>

